headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Paycom Software Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Paycom Software has underperformed the broader market over the past year, yet analysts remain moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Citigroup Maintains Neutral on Paycom Software, Lowers Price Target to $128
summary: Citigroup  analyst Steven Enders   maintains Paycom Software (NYSE:PAYC) with a Neutral and lowers the price target from $185 to $128.
